<br>
Broken golem was cake. the hard part is just getting him to spawn. I believe its a 2 day timer. hes got 250k hps and is straight melee. I did the turn in and the MA was there to gain aggro. Didnt get hit once.<br>
<br>
VS, well honestly I got lucky this was about 4 months ago but I had friends in high places and got him manaburned and somehow got the merit on it through wheel and dealing even though there was a wizzy there who had tried 8 times and it hadnt dropped.<br>
<br>
So of course since I got that so easy, Phinny had to be a major pain in the ass.<br>
<br>
Checking on him:<br>
make an alt ranger get them an eb cast on them and go to the entrance of kedge. I had a lvl 2 ranger. sort track by reverse conside if phinny is up he will be at the top. make a track sit and camp hot key. you can check all you want with this even if eb runs out. just sit and camp immediately then hit track. my alt camped with 2 air bubs alot and it resets every time you log.<br>
<br>
Getting to him:<br>
Its actually pretty easy. go down the center tunnel one lvl. go south and down. get to the shark room and go right. go all the way down your first chance. then go all the way up a long tunnel to another shark room. go wes. next room go right and you will have one way to get to the phinny ledge.<br>
<br>
Checking for the staff with your wizzy:<br>
Well i never actually saw him weilding the staff cause i ended up mqing it but go down there and cast eye of zomm/tallon from the ledge. go into the star shaped hole. last time i checked phinny was in a cubby not moving possibly cause he was able to be solo pulled when he wandered? anyways if he has a small staff with a blue tip that is the chanter tash stick. if it is a trident its the rogue piercer. if it looks like the chanter rod of insiduous (sp?) glamour then its the shammy malo stick. from what i hear if he has a long staff like the staff of the wheel thats the one. I only heard of him having it once in 4 months. I killed him 11 times and checked for him weilding at least 11-13 times. so i would have been at kill count 24 possibly. There were many times i saved my friends a hastle by checkig if he was weilding. then someone else brought a whole raid only to be let down.<br>
<br>
who do i need:<br>
you need at lead a monk/sk to pull, a cleric, and someone to cc. druids bards and chanters work well. they are easy to tank even for a well equiped monk.<br>
<br>
pulling:<br>
pull counter clockwise when puling swirlspine seahorses. more that one is hard more than 2 is death with a weak group. pull at 6 9 12 3 on the &quot;clock&quot; then pull phinny you will get the guardians unless you got Tazer(prexus) pulling for you. he singled phinny with 3 seahorses only got adds cause we got off the ramp too far in the room. still not sure how he did it.<br>
<br>
seahorses cant be mezed and are highly MR guardians can be mezed and are easier.<br>
<br>
If phinny didnt have ching buddies then a cleric/wizzy could probaby duo him, yeah hes that much of a wuss.<br>
<br>
drops:<br>
11 kills<br>
chanter staff : at least 10<br>
shammy staff: 5 once was a double<br>
mage staff: 3 once was double<br>
kedge robe :3-4 im wearing it cause no one needed it<br>
backbone:2 or 3 <br>
fusible ore: all<br>
bcs :0<br>
<br>
many times if you just kill without checking you will get disappointed by only having the chanter staff drop, i did.<br>
<br>
finally sucked it up and did the mq with a friend who had the staff drop when i wasnt online. <br>
<br>
I did the first part of the shammy epic for faction. have you and a chanter bind in nfp by the barbarian for the turn in. port to gfay kill peg leg charm and say &quot;i wish to know more&quot; then gate invis and turn in. repeat till you dont  need the chanter.<br>
<br>
I did this to amiable, my friend was ally being a shammy, we did the mq fine and i got my epic. hope this helps you all out and hope they up the phinny drop rate or spawn timer. its so hard getting a phinny group at 5am.<br>
<br>
